      <description>&lt;figure&gt;
    &lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;6QGo44.gif&#34;/&gt; 
&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Haunted West is a game made in 5 days during a school workshop. It is a top view 4 directional shooter where you must survive against hordes of angry ghosts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Btn play&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Gallery/carrousel assets&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It was made using processing, a javascript based ide mainly used to create procedurally generated art.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
